{"tid":634784,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"何君堯曾樹和鼓吹港獨份子殺無赦 警查7個月不起訴","createTime":"2018-04-19T14:17:30.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-20T02:21:14.000Z","uid":39464,"like":2,"dislike":36,"uniUserReply":14,"replies":[{"pid":"4bb1e0fb24d38f5819b9dc2668ab3b25a7705ba1","tid":634784,"uid":39464,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:17:30.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://static.appledaily.hk/images/e-paper/20180419/large/1524147015_8a03.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.appledaily.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20180419%2Flarge%2F1524147015_8a03.png&h=c26b89c9&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n建制派議員何君堯和鄉事派曾樹和去年9月在反戴耀廷集會上，大聲疾呼要對港獨份子「殺、無赦」。警方事隔7個月後完成調查，稱證據不足以對任何人提出起訴，但指若將來得到更多資料顯示有人涉案，會覆核案件。<br />\n<br />\n屏山鄉鄉事委員會主席曾樹和及建制派立法會議員何君堯，去年9月在「革走戴耀廷吶喊大會」上發言，其中曾樹和指對「搞港獨」人士「我哋必須要殺！」。在旁的何君堯則附和：「無赦。」何會見傳媒時更補充：「呢啲人（港獨份子）唔殺咗佢做咩？」事後行政會議成員湯家驊一度稱有關言論或觸犯《公安條例》，並有市民向警方報案。警方當時表示，交由港島總區刑事總部公眾活動調查組跟進。<br />\n警方近日以電郵回覆電子報案人士，指已就何君堯及曾樹和於當日言論完成調查，但稱「調查所得之證據並不足以對任何人提出起訴」。警方補充，若將來得到更多資料顯示有人涉案，警方會覆核案件。<br />\n另外，該封由港島總區刑事總部發出的電郵，警員涉未有以「密件副本（bcc）」形式發送，令收到該封回覆電郵的報案人電郵地址全數曝光，至少50多人受影響。<br />\n《蘋果》已向警方查詢，暫未獲回覆。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180419/58094652\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180419%2F58094652&d=odlsMY%2FUvJxbsnYOIisLTAhMEkA7P3Wv%2FuCJwdwWxT4%3D&h=c44ebe60\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Flocal%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180419%2F58094652&h=1c701f58\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/local/realtime/article/20180419/58094652</a>"},{"pid":"fc9034cb8a5836868efe9839da02a78822388144","tid":634784,"uid":44358,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:34:09.000Z","msg":"仆街，中伏了<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"95c4cb9f05a62a0c858647583eed9f246c2add88","tid":634784,"uid":77196,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T14:57:30.000Z","msg":"好明顯專登唔保密，等果兩條友可以殺無赦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c2eaa6821635a75011c11955b8d1c21467df268e","tid":634784,"uid":2697,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:04:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fuck.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"199308f5414c8feae00d90f9b9f18ebfc1da3b1c","tid":634784,"uid":55913,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T15:48:24.000Z","msg":"有撚查過"},{"pid":"78fb865fa5011a01f9e35aab1bc56851cff2d055","tid":634784,"uid":157362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:03:41.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"6ab0b4c60ebebe42fdb0731986dcab91124113dc","tid":634784,"uid":173849,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:19:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"29a796c95a45ddfadd6ad757287ea39e172a66ab","tid":634784,"uid":173002,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-19T16:37:10.000Z","msg":"七警案有大批五毛示威者侮辱主審法官，律政司宜家都無提調查進度。 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ee6b4dc2619e5e9cf97e50b3a5f6ba85401dbf53","tid":634784,"uid":41821,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:50:24.000Z","msg":"自己友緊係who fucking cares喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"67f6e7968db1cead67aaf56f3930925b39281363","tid":634784,"uid":34103,"like":0,"dislike":4,"score":-4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T00:56:47.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"4feee18b6deb0d2d7f5044a1087e969d5a39d736","tid":634784,"uid":33668,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-20T02:08:09.000Z","msg":"有冇人UPDATE去佢個律司會講下"},{"pid":"